  "en": {
    "title": "env - Show environment variables",
    "synopsis": "env",
    "description": "List all active environment variables of the shell session.",
    "details": "NAME\n  env - Show active environment variables.\n\nSYNOPSIS\n  env\n\nDESCRIPTION\n  Outputs system environment variables formatted as 'KEY=VALUE' rows.\n\nSYSTEM ARCHITECTURE\n  Reads and parses properties from the local 'envVars' runtime memory object.\n\nEXIT CODES\n  0\n    Success.\n\nCONFORMING TO\n  NucleoOS extension compatible with POSIX.\n\nAUTHOR\n  NucleoOS Core Devs.\n\nREPORTING BUGS\n  Report bugs to support@nucleoos.org.\n\nSEE ALSO\n  export(1)\n\nADVANCED EXAMPLES\n  env"
